went from room to room, that

00:36:53.360 --> 00:36:55.640
the taste of the drink in
their glass changed

00:36:55.640 --> 00:36:56.890
by as much as 20%.

00:36:56.890 --> 00:36:58.040
The glass was always
in their hand.

00:36:58.040 --> 00:37:00.030
