the scorecards, they were

00:37:00.030 --> 00:37:02.300
giving the same drink a
different taste, hence

00:37:02.300 --> 00:37:06.010
demonstrating, we think, the
importance of the atmosphere

00:37:06.010 --> 00:37:08.610
as part of what contemporary
people think of as

00:37:08.610 --> 00:37:10.850
the taste of food.

00:37:10.850 --> 00:37:11.120
Thank you.

00:37:11.120 --> 00:37:19.610
[APPLAUSE]

